      <prop type="x-target-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">易經 5 judgment</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">易經 5 judgment</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>需，有孚，光亨，貞吉。利涉大川。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>Xu intimates that, with the sincerity which is declared in it, there will be brilliant success. With firmness there will be good fortune; and it will be advantageous to cross the great stream.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
