      <prop type="x-source-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-target-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">易經 5 初九</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">易經 5 初九</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>初九，需于郊，利用恆，无咎。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The first NINE, undivided, shows its subject waiting in the distant border. It will be well for him constantly to maintain (the purpose thus shown), in which case there will be no error.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
