      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">易經 5 九二</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">易經 5 九二</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>九二，需于沙，小有言，終吉。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The second NINE, undivided, shows its subject waiting on the sand (of the mountain stream). He will (suffer) the small (injury of) being spoken (against), but in the end there will be good fortune.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
