      <prop type="x-translation-ref">易經 5 九三</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>九三，需于泥，致寇至。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The third NINE, undivided, shows its subject in the mud (close by the stream). He thereby invites the approach of injury.</seg>
      </tuv>
