      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>六四，需于血，出自穴。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The fourth SIX, divided, shows its subject waiting in (the place of) blood. But he will get out of the cavern.</seg>
