      <prop type="x-translation-ref">易經 5 九五</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>九五，需于酒食，貞吉。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The fifth NINE, undivided, shows its subject waiting amidst the appliances of a feast. Through his firmness and correctness there will be good fortune.</seg>
      </tuv>
