      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">易經 5 上六</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">易經 5 上六</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>上六，入于穴，有不速之客三人來，敬之終吉。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The topmost SIX, divided, shows its subject entered into the cavern. (But) there are three guests coming, without being urged, (to his help). If he receive them respectfully, there will be good fortune in the end.</seg>
      </tuv>
